  <title xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Red Barnet - NGO Call Afghanistan 2022-2023</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The grant is awarded to the Save the Children Denmark project: Provision of quality education and child protection support to promote the safety and well-being of crisis-affected and marginalised girls, boys, their families and communities in Afghanistan.

The stated objective of the project is: To improve access to education and child protection services for at risk and vulnerable boys and girls in Nangarhar and Kunar.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To improve access to education and child protection services for at risk and vulnerable boys and girls in the provinces Nangarhar and Kunar. The integrated package of services will address underlying vulnerabilities and risks due to conflicts. Boys and girls will have access to education facilities and child protection services to provide them with basic psychosocial support to improve resilience and wellbeing.</narrative>
  </description>
